{
  "stories": [
    {
      "id": 101,
      "title": {
        "en": "The Alien's Ice Cream Adventure 👽",
        "hi": "एलियन का आइसक्रीम एडवेंचर 👽"
      },
      "genre": {
        "en": "Science & Fun",
        "hi": "विज्ञान और मज़ा"
      },
      "pages": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Zog the little green alien landed on Earth. He was very hot.",
            "image": "https://nayansrivastav.github.io/ANS/assets/story_cats.webp",
            "audio": "https://nayansrivastav.github.io/ANS/assets/audio/story_101_en_0.mp3"
          },
          {
            "text": "He saw a sweet colorful food called ice cream and took a big bite.",
            "image": "https://nayansrivastav.github.io/ANS/assets/story_hippo.webp",
            "audio": "https://nayansrivastav.github.io/ANS/assets/audio/story_101_en_1.mp3"
          },
          {
            "text": "Brain freeze! Zog's antenna turned blue, but he loved the sweet taste.",
            "image": "https://nayansrivastav.github.io/ANS/assets/story_cats.webp",
            "audio": "https://nayansrivastav.github.io/ANS/assets/audio/story_101_en_2.mp3"
          }
        ],
        "hi": [
          {
            "text": "ज़ोग नाम का छोटा हरा एलियन पृथ्वी पर उतरा। उसे बहुत गर्मी लग रही थी।",
            "image": "https://nayansrivastav.github.io/ANS/assets/story_cats.webp",
            "audio": "https://nayansrivastav.github.io/ANS/assets/audio/story_101_hi_0.mp3"
          },
          {
            "text": "उसने आइसक्रीम नामक एक मीठा रंगीन भोजन देखा और एक बड़ा निवाला खा लिया।",
            "image": "https://nayansrivastav.github.io/ANS/assets/story_hippo.webp",
            "audio": "https://nayansrivastav.github.io/ANS/assets/audio/story_101_hi_1.mp3"
          },
          {
            "text": "दिमाग जम गया! ज़ोग का एंटीना नीला हो गया, लेकिन उसे मीठा स्वाद बहुत पसंद आया।",
            "image": "https://nayansrivastav.github.io/ANS/assets/story_cats.webp",
            "audio": "https://nayansrivastav.github.io/ANS/assets/audio/story_101_hi_2.mp3"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 102,
      "title": {
        "en": "The Clever Monkey & The Crocodile 🐵",
        "hi": "चतुर बंदर और मगरमच्छ 🐵"
      },
      "genre": {
        "en": "Folk Tales",
        "hi": "लोक कथाएँ"
      },
      "pages": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Mintu the clever monkey lived on a sweet berry tree near the river.",
            "image": "https://nayansrivastav.github.io/ANS/assets/story_monkey.webp",
            "audio": "https://nayansrivastav.github.io/ANS/assets/audio/story_102_en_0.mp3"
          },
          {
            "text": "A crocodile named Crocky wanted to catch Mintu for lunch.",
            "image": "https://nayansrivastav.github.io/ANS/assets/story_croc.webp",
            "audio": "https://nayansrivastav.github.io/ANS/assets/audio/story_102_en_1.mp3"
          },
          {
            "text": "Mintu tricked Crocky and jumped back to his tree safely. Clever Mintu!",
            "image": "https://nayansrivastav.github.io/ANS/assets/story_monkey.webp",
            "audio": "https://nayansrivastav.github.io/ANS/assets/audio/story_102_en_2.mp3"
          }
        ],
        "hi": [
          {
            "text": "मिंटू नाम का चतुर बंदर नदी के किनारे एक मीठे जामुन के पेड़ पर रहता था।",
            "image": "https://nayansrivastav.github.io/ANS/assets/story_monkey.webp",
            "audio": "https://nayansrivastav.github.io/ANS/assets/audio/story_102_hi_0.mp3"
          },
          {
            "text": "क्रॉकी नाम का मगरमच्छ मिंटू को दोपहर के भोजन के लिए पकड़ना चाहता था।",
            "image": "https://nayansrivastav.github.io/ANS/assets/story_croc.webp",
            "audio": "https://nayansrivastav.github.io/ANS/assets/audio/story_102_hi_1.mp3"
          },
          {
            "text": "मिंटू ने क्रॉकी को चकमा दिया और सुरक्षित रूप से अपने पेड़ पर कूद गया। चतुर मिंटू!",
            "image": "https://nayansrivastav.github.io/ANS/assets/story_monkey.webp",
            "audio": "https://nayansrivastav.github.io/ANS/assets/audio/story_102_hi_2.mp3"
          }
        ]
      }
    }
  ]
}